{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act37side_level_act37side_03_beg","storyGroup":"act37side","storySort":6,"storyDependence":"act37side_level_act37side_02_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"GO-3","storyName":"议会公决","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"战时，当典范军刚刚攻入城内的时候，维娜收到了一份神秘的礼物，那是她第一次确认了一位好友的幸存。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act37side/level_act37side_03_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act37side_03","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":4,"next":6,"characters":["担忧的佣兵","“铣痕”","？？？","娜汀","神秘的血魔","克洛维希娅","摩根","维娜","警惕的佣兵"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"image","image":"55_i17_2","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":8},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":10},{"type":"sticker","id":11,"multi":"true","text":"<i>当我决定为阿勒黛撰写一个单独的篇章时，一直没法弄出个满意的开头，因为我突然发现，自己对这个非常熟悉的名字简直一无所知。</i>","x":"300","y":"240","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":12,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>坎伯兰家的最后一个人，背叛了我们，却又甘愿为了救我们而牺牲的人，也是喜欢夸耀自己做的奶油炖菜汤美味的人。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":13},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":14},{"type":"sticker","id":15,"multi":"true","text":"<i>“铣痕”......开斯特的手下......“永远高洁的坎伯兰”......到底哪一个才是真正的她？</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":16},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":18},{"type":"dialog","id":19},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":20},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"image","id":23},{"type":"charslot","id":24},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/28/Avg_bg_bg_cherunder_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":25},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.5","block":"true","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":27},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loading_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_sys_loading_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":28,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":30},{"type":"dialog","id":31},{"type":"animtext","id":32,"name":"group_location_stamp","style":"avg_both","pos":"-400,-200","block":"false","text":"<p=1>伦蒂尼姆地下隧道</><p=2>1098年9月28日 4:53 P.M.</>"},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":33},{"type":"animtextclean","id":34},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":35},{"type":"text","text":"距离典范军突破城内封锁还有34分钟","id":36},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"老大，坐标确认，那个匿名讯息警告的地点就在前面。信息来源刚刚也查清楚了，是——","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"罗德岛。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e1/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"没什么好惊讶的，对我来说这不难猜。走吧。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":44},{"type":"text","text":"佣兵犹豫地站在原地。","id":45},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"......说。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"弟兄们一直很信你。没有你，我们这些人不是烂在小巷里，就是被魔族佬——","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"反正都是死过一次的人，我不介意为了你拼拼命。但这事没道理，罗德岛我们根本不认识，凭什么信他们。","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"现在那支典范军就快突进城里了，眼看外面就该彻底乱起来了。我们趁着这机会明明能捞很多好处......","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"或者......至少你不该亲自来冒这个险。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"不止你这么想吧？","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":55},{"type":"charslot","id":56},{"type":"text","text":"佣兵沉默，他不敢直视“铣痕”的眼睛，他害怕她发怒。","id":57},{"type":"text","text":"但等了一会儿，什么也没发生。","id":58},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"这场仗打完之后，你们想过伦蒂尼姆会怎么样吗？","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"呃......和之前一样......吗？","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"不，没有什么会再和以前一样。无论这场仗结果如何，谁都回不去了。","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"等等，老大，你想扔下我们？！","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"不，我需要你们。很快，伦蒂尼姆会变成一座亟需被缝补的城市。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"过去的秩序已经被暴力和死亡摧毁，而留下的那些缺口，足够喂饱我们了。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"可——","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"我现在没在问你的意见。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"听好了，我不打算继续过以往那种生活，那就得早为将来做打算。当然，我不会忘了你们。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"但想保住这口肉，就得让人知道我们能做到什么，敢做什么。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"别说你们没得选。现在，你是继续走，还是回头？","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"......","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"他妈的，我走前面，老大。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":80},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":81},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":82},{"type":"charslot","id":83},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_bg_27_g7_subway.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":84},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":86},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cavewaterdrop","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":87},{"type":"soundvolume","channel":"a","volume":"0.7","fadetime":"2","id":88},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":90},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"我没看错吧......这些是什么东西......","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"钢架缝隙还有炉子里的那些血红色石头，这些都是魔族佬藏在这的？！他们到底想干嘛......","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"......血魔的东西。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":96},{"type":"charslot","id":97},{"type":"text","text":"空气中弥漫着淡淡的血腥气味，她想起了那些如噩梦般涌来的蠕动的怪物。","id":98},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"老大！这边，我找到点东西！","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"这是......公爵联军的士兵？","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"不对劲，刚死不久。这里还有铭牌......联军第八纵队第五步兵团......校官？！","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"马奇伯爵的部队，诺曼底公爵的人？身上没有伤口。不是被人谋害，但也绝对不是自然死亡。","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"据我所知，这支部队现在明明还在城墙外围城，一个校官为什么会出现在这——","id":107,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":108},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"1","id":109},{"type":"dialog","id":110},{"type":"charslot","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哪来的？直接动手速战速决，不要耽误执行命令。","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"还有其他祭坛需要启动，剩下的时间不多。","id":113},{"type":"dialog","id":114},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$escape_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_dia_escape_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":115,"musicid":2},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_armour","volume":"1","id":116},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1341_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1341_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":119},{"type":"charslot","id":120},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"这些该死的魔族佬把我们包围了。怎么撤——","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":123},{"type":"charslot","id":124},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#8$1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","focus":"all","id":125},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":126},{"type":"dialog","id":127},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovementsp","volume":"1","id":128},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_stmwpn_d2","volume":"0.7","delay":"0.3","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#8$2","duration":"1","focus":"all","id":130},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":131},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#8$2","focus":"m","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"为什么要撤？","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":134},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"......","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":137},{"type":"charslot","id":138},{"type":"text","text":"“疯子”。","id":139},{"type":"text","text":"没人知道她手中那柄属于蒸汽骑士的锋刃从何而来，更遑论“铣痕”的出身。","id":140},{"type":"text","text":"佣兵的腿在抖，他很后悔。几分钟前，他本有机会活着转身就走。","id":141},{"type":"text","text":"......只要那柄紫色的锋刃不会从背后捅了他。","id":142},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"妈的。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":145},{"type":"charslot","id":146},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"c","id":147},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"c","fadetime":"2","id":148},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1333_1#4$1","duration":"1","id":149},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":150},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1333_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜汀","text":"哦？我认得这个武器。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_avg_npc_1333_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1333_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜汀","text":"将军给我的情报里提到了你。这么有恃无恐，难道那个大铁皮罐头也在附近吗？","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_avg_npc_1333_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1333_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜汀","text":"说不定这次能一并解决另一个麻烦。","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_1333_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#6$2","focus":"m","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"啧。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":159},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1333_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":160},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":161},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_stmwpn_d1","volume":"1","id":162},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_stmwpn_n","volume":"1","loop":"false","channel":"atk","delay":"0.18","id":163},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_runstop","volume":"1","delay":"0.5","id":164},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":165},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"jump","posto":"-80,0","afrom":"1","ato":"0","power":"10","times":"1","duration":"0.3","id":166},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":167},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":168},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.8","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":169},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":171},{"type":"charslot","id":172},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1333_1#3$1","duration":"0.5","id":173},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":174},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1333_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜汀","text":"呵，你们继续手里的任务，别管我——","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1333_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"charslot","id":178},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.11","fadetime":"0.7","id":179},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.11","fadetime":"0.7","id":180},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":181},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_doorbell","volume":"0.2","id":182},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":183},{"type":"text","text":"“叮铃铃”。","id":184},{"type":"text","text":"好似微风拂动陵墓梁上的风铃，安眠者面纱上垂下的金坠与宝石在空中摇曳，撞击。","id":185},{"type":"dialog","id":186},{"type":"curtain","fadetime":"1","id":187},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":188},{"type":"dialog","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"抱歉，各位，请问有谁见过我丢失的耳坠吗？","id":190},{"type":"dialog","id":191},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"找到你了，小石榴——碎，碎掉了......","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"那只好借用一下你的玩具了，杜卡雷。不过反正你也没法拒绝嘛。","id":194},{"type":"dialog","id":195},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_originiumcastshort","volume":"0.6","id":196},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":197},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_blodmgicrclrlp","channel":"bd","loop":"true","volume":"0","id":198},{"type":"soundvolume","channel":"bd","volume":"1","fadetime":"1","id":199},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_blodmgic_2","id":200},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":201},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":203},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_glassbroken","id":205},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":206},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_statueshake","volume":"0.6","id":207},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_statuecollapse","volume":"0.9","delay":"1","id":208},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":209},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1.5","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":210},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":211},{"type":"text","text":"钢铁间的血色祭坛方才泛起了光芒，却又立马黯淡，直至碎裂。","id":212},{"type":"text","text":"而空中那几乎崩解为碎片的血红耳坠却氤氲着微光，复原如新。","id":213},{"type":"text","text":"殷红炫目，不禁令人心神摇曳。","id":214},{"type":"dialog","id":215},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bd","fadetime":"1","id":216},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":217},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_doorbell","volume":"0.5","id":218},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":219},{"type":"text","text":"“叮铃铃”。","id":220},{"type":"text","text":"响声在“铣痕”的耳边回荡。","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"先替我保管好小石榴。","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"她会引你们去该去的地方，现在，你们该走了。","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不过真奇怪，凯尔希勋爵那样的人居然会相信你。","id":224},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#4$2","focus":"m","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"——！","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":228},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":229},{"type":"charslot","id":230},{"type":"image","image":"55_i04","screenadapt":"coverall","id":231},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":233},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_darkness_03_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":234,"musicid":3},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_batflypast","volume":"0.6","id":235},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"120","yFrom":"-50","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"12","block":"false","id":236},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":238},{"type":"text","text":"她看到了那个红与黑的身影。","id":239},{"type":"text","text":"血魔。血魔为什么要救我？凯尔希勋爵？罗德岛的凯尔希医生？她们到底想要做什么？","id":240},{"type":"text","text":"她有太多的困惑。可不知何时，她的手中已经握着那枚冷冽的锥形耳坠。","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的血魔","text":"如果你还想帮上那人的忙，就该抓紧时间了，这附近的祭坛可不止这一处。","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"......我该怎么做？","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的血魔","text":"她会告诉你。","id":244},{"type":"text","text":"“她”？“铣痕”突然感受到了手中耳坠的震动，如同心跳。","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜汀","text":"拦下她——","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的血魔","text":"嘘。","id":247},{"type":"dialog","id":248},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_blood","volume":"0.7","id":249},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":250},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":251},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.3","id":252},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_heartbeat","channel":"ht","loop":"false","volume":"0.8","id":253},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"ht","fadetime":"2","id":254},{"type":"image","image":"55_i04","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.02","yScale":"1.02","fadetime":"0.3","id":255},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":256},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.6","id":257},{"type":"image","image":"55_i04","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0.6","id":258},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜汀","text":"*萨卡兹粗口*！","id":260},{"type":"text","text":"娜汀能感觉到全身的血液在刹那间向心脏倒流，晕眩感陡然降临。","id":261},{"type":"text","text":"她第一次羡慕那些已经抛弃了血肉之躯的同族们。","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的血魔","text":"路为你留好了。","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的血魔","text":"保护好她，她会引你来见我。","id":264},{"type":"dialog","id":265},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":266},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":268},{"type":"image","id":269},{"type":"charslot","id":270},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b7/Avg_bg_27_g6_hideout.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.5","block":"true","id":272},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":273},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loading_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_sys_loading_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":274,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":275},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":276},{"type":"dialog","id":277},{"type":"animtext","id":278,"name":"group_location_stamp","style":"avg_only_medium","pos":"-400,-200","block":"false","text":"<p=2>1098年9月28日 5:21 P.M.</>"},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":279},{"type":"animtextclean","id":280},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":281},{"type":"text","text":"距离典范军突破城内封锁还有6分钟","id":282},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"走吧，该去下一个地方了。","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"老大，那个血魔的东西太诡异了。破坏掉那些祭坛后，它变得越来越......漂亮了。","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"顾不上了。通讯里说，典范军的队伍明明已经突进到了城内，却反而被公爵联军给拦了下来，事情恐怕有变化。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"命令传到工厂那边的人手里了吗？","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"传到了，他们在准备了。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"这些藏起来的奇怪萨卡兹祭坛，还有突然传开的公爵们要封锁抛弃整个伦蒂尼姆的流言......","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"哼，我已经拿不准，真正想对这座城市动手的是谁了。","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":297},{"type":"charslot","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你真的还在乎是谁吗？","id":299},{"type":"dialog","id":300},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_401_1#10$1","duration":"0.7","id":301},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":302},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_401_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"好久不见，阿勒黛。","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"......","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"我以为你死了。","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_401_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"我也一样。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"你不可能短时间内解决这些麻烦，哪怕有罗德岛的协助也不行。","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_401_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"萨卡兹在城内经营了这么多年，藏了不知道多少祭坛。能瞒过我，只靠他们自己不可能做到。","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"放任这些祭坛启动，恐怕足以摧毁伦蒂尼姆的几个核心区域。不过，我已经找到几个关键节点并且清理掉了。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"单靠你自己......？","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_401_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"维娜需要帮助，典范军还差了最后一口气。公爵们需要听到一些真实的声音。","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"至于公爵们准备抛弃伦蒂尼姆的消息，是我散开的，它也并非完全的流言。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"......你想让我干什么？","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_401_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"你已经在做了，不是吗？你的人手都已经动了起来。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"只是你们都还需要被推一把。我会帮你处理剩下的祭坛。","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"你......变化很大。","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_401_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"你不也一样吗，“铣痕”。你真的喜欢现在的名字吗？","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_401_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":328},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":329},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":330},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"你选择了活下去，那就走下去看看这条路的终点在哪里。","id":332},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"......","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担忧的佣兵","text":"老大，她是——","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"走，以最快的速度赶到外围城区，通知其他人就位——准备接应典范军。","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":339},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":340},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":341},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"charslot","id":343},{"type":"image","image":"55_i05_1","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":344},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":345},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":346},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":347,"musicid":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":348},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":349},{"type":"dialog","id":350},{"type":"animtext","id":351,"name":"group_location_stamp","style":"avg_both","pos":"-400,-200","block":"false","text":"<p=1>伦蒂尼姆</><p=2>1098年9月28日 5:27 P.M.</>"},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":352},{"type":"animtextclean","id":353},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":354},{"type":"text","text":"典范军突破城内封锁，全城的工厂在怒吼中重启，迎接回家的人。","id":355},{"type":"dialog","id":356},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":357},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":358},{"type":"sticker","id":359,"multi":"true","text":"<i>我总是反反复复想起那个下午。</i>","x":"300","y":"240","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":360,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>工厂，维娜，蒸汽，欢呼，拳赛，怒吼，贝尔德......</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":361,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>所有的记忆里的碎片总会一股脑地涌出来，混杂在一起，然后让我彻底记不清那个下午的所有细节。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":362},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":363},{"type":"sticker","id":364,"multi":"true","text":"<i>我唯一忘不掉的是，维娜说，我们到家了。</i>","x":"300","y":"240","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":365,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>我想哭，这条路走了好久，好远......从城内到城外，从战场到家乡......</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":366,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>我们回家了，可支持着我们一路走来的人，又失去了多少呢？</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":367},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":368},{"type":"sticker","id":369,"multi":"true","text":"<i>除了阿勒黛，又还有谁能离去后又回来呢？</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":370,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>......</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":371},{"type":"sticker","id":372,"multi":"true","text":"<i>我想贝尔德了。</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":373},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":374},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":375},{"type":"dialog","id":376},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":377},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":378},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":379},{"type":"image","id":380},{"type":"charslot","id":381},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_bg_32_g4_ordnancefactory.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":382},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.5","block":"true","id":383},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":384},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":385,"musicid":6},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":386},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":387},{"type":"dialog","id":388},{"type":"animtext","id":389,"name":"group_location_stamp","style":"avg_both","pos":"-400,-200","block":"false","text":"<p=1>典范军临时阵地</><p=2>1098年9月30日 5:22 A.M.</>"},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":390},{"type":"animtextclean","id":391},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":392},{"type":"text","text":"距离典范军突破城内封锁已经过去2天","id":393},{"type":"dialog","id":394},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"原来物资清点是这么痛苦的事情吗？","id":396,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"过去盘算我们地盘里厂子的物资也没有这么磨人吧......","id":397,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"这要是算痛苦的话，我倒希望能再苦一点。","id":399,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"嘿嘿，不过确实蛮让人兴奋的，原来还有这么多人愿意支持我们——","id":401,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":402},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"（哈欠）折腾太久了，都天亮了。","id":403,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f3/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......得加快速度了，不能拖太久。其他人能为我们争取的时间不会太多。","id":405,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"按维什戴尔那边传回来的消息，军事委员会的整个指挥系统被他们搅了个乱七八糟，但食腐者军队还在西部大堂区域严阵以待。","id":406,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我们进城已经两天，但他们至今还没大动静。","id":407,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"不是有消息说特雷西斯已经抛下他们躲起来了吗？说不定食腐者他们一直没动静就是这个原因。","id":409,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"只是猜测而已，甚至连博士他们都还没有确切的消息可以证实这个说法。","id":411,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"摩根，去休息一下吧。联军的总攻信号很快就会来了——","id":413,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"维娜，我只是没那么喜欢点数！","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"......我想去帮达格达。至少在说服更多市民加入我们抢回场子这件事上，我比她更有经验。","id":417,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"戴菲恩在说服那些犹豫的贵族，汉娜和凯瑟琳在联合剩余的工人和自救军，我相信她们都能搞定。","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#13$1","focus":"m","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"但达格达......不是适合这种任务的性子，她......","id":420,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"去吧。","id":422,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":423},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#13$1","focus":"m","id":424},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":425},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":426},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":427},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walkfast","volume":"0.7","id":428},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":429},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":430},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"呼。","id":432,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f9/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":433},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":434},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cardboard","volume":"1","id":435},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":436},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"继续吧。这边是海蒂小姐支援的物资......还有这些自救军偷偷造的武器......","id":438,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":439},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":440},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"嗯？","id":442,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"压在最下面......这是谁送过来的？清单里没有啊？","id":443,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":444},{"type":"charslot","id":445},{"type":"text","text":"她环顾了四周，除了来往搬运物资的典范军成员，她没有发现任何身份不明的人。","id":446},{"type":"dialog","id":447},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_open_box","volume":"1","id":448},{"type":"text","text":"在警惕地确认这份来源不明的物资并无威胁后，维娜好奇地打开了箱子，取出了其中的东西。","id":449},{"type":"text","text":"她愣住了。","id":450},{"type":"dialog","id":451},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_calm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":452,"musicid":7},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0.5","keep":"true","initamount":"0.5","amount":"0","block":"false","id":453},{"type":"image","image":"55_i03_1","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"3","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","y":"50","id":454},{"type":"imagetween","image":"55_i03_1","fadetime":"0.5","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","yTo":"0","duration":"15","id":455},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":456},{"type":"text","text":"一套......衣服？","id":457},{"type":"text","text":"初升太阳的光线仍然带有一丝寒意，落在了一枚家徽之上——","id":458},{"type":"text","text":"“维多利亚家族”，她的家族。","id":459},{"type":"text","text":"维娜感到了愤怒，这是什么卑劣的恶作剧吗？","id":460},{"type":"text","text":"不......不对——","id":461},{"type":"text","text":"她摩挲着这套衣物，她认得它的样式......它曾属于维多利亚的王室。","id":462},{"type":"text","text":"可它为什么会出现在这里？是谁找到了它，又将它送到自己手中？","id":463},{"type":"text","text":"在她的脑海中，只有一个名字。","id":464},{"type":"dialog","id":465},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":466},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":467},{"type":"image","id":468},{"type":"charslot","id":469},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/98/Avg_bg_32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":470},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","id":471},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","id":472},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":473},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":474},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":475},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"走吧，差不多了。","id":477,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":478},{"type":"dialogue","name":"警惕的佣兵","text":"老大，情况如何？","id":479,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"他们的战备资源比起联军要差上不少。那些公爵们铁了心让典范军打头阵，他们的伤亡不会小......","id":481,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"......但对他们来说是一个机会。","id":482,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"公爵们想要一个英雄，民众们需要一个英雄，那我何不帮这段故事再添加一点风味呢？","id":484,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"警惕的佣兵","text":"你想赌他们能赢。","id":486,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":487},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"赌？不，点数早在城墙下那场大战结束时就注定了。现在，无非是各方趁着最后的时机来加注罢了。","id":488,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":489},{"type":"dialogue","name":"警惕的佣兵","text":"哈，我不懂，反正信你就对了。接下来该干嘛？","id":490,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":491},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"杀人。","id":492,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"等决战一起，城里该乱起来了。想趁着这时候“干点大事”的人不会少，但我不想看到有人把手伸到我的面前来。","id":493,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1342_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":494},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1342_1#1$1","focus":"all","id":495},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":496},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_openftstpwalk","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"walk1","id":497},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","loop":"true","channel":"walk2","volume":"0.4","delay":"0.3","id":498},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"walk1","fadetime":"3","id":499},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"walk2","fadetime":"3","id":500},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":501},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":502},{"type":"dialogue","name":"警惕的佣兵","text":"......话说，老大，你留下的东西到底是个啥？","id":503},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"呵，让传说更有说服力的道具——","id":504},{"type":"dialog","id":505},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":506},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":507},{"type":"charslot","id":508},{"type":"image","image":"55_i03_1","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":509},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":510},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":511},{"type":"text","text":"“属于王室的衣服，从坎伯兰公爵府废墟里抢救出来的。那位典范军的首领能用上。”","id":512},{"type":"text","text":"“先王的遗孤回到故土，以王的姿态驱逐魔族......你不喜欢这个故事吗？”","id":513},{"type":"text","text":"“可老大......我听说她挺瞧不上这名头？”","id":514},{"type":"text","text":"“如果她真想说服那些还在摇摆的人，她就需要这个名头......”","id":515},{"type":"text","text":"“至少现在需要。”","id":516},{"type":"dialog","id":517},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":518},{"type":"text","text":"她是否还活着——","id":519},{"type":"text","text":"自蒸汽骑士再度出现那天起，维娜的心中便一直存在着某个侥幸。或许身边的人心中都有，但没人会说出来。","id":520},{"type":"text","text":"她紧张地环顾了周围，却没有看到那个人的身影......","id":521},{"type":"text","text":"维娜反倒松了一口气，她完全没有准备好。","id":522},{"type":"dialog","id":523},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper2","volume":"1","id":524},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":525},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......一张纸条？","id":526},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"“按你的尺寸改了改，希望还合身。”","id":527},{"type":"dialog","id":528},{"type":"image","image":"55_i03_2","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":529},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":530},{"type":"text","text":"没有落款。","id":531},{"type":"text","text":"但她却终于第一次能够确认，阿勒黛，还活着。","id":532},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......","id":533},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"里面还有其他东西？这是——","id":534},{"type":"text","text":"几张照片，还有写在背后的几句话。","id":535},{"type":"text","text":"“顺便找到些说不定对你有用的证据，是关于某位公爵的。”","id":536},{"type":"dialog","id":537},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":538},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":539},{"type":"charslot","id":540},{"type":"image","id":541}],"characters":["担忧的佣兵","“铣痕”","？？？","娜汀","神秘的血魔","克洛维希娅","摩根","维娜","警惕的佣兵"]}